        </div>
        
        <div class="info-row"><span>è»Œé“çˆ¬å‡å¡åº¦ï¼š</span><span id="v-deg" class="data">45</span>Â°</div>
        <input type="range" min="15" max="85" value="45" id="degSlider">

        <button id="arrowToggleBtn" class="btn-toggle">ğŸ‘ï¸ é¡¯ç¤ºå‘é‡ç®­é ­ï¼šON</button>

        <div class="legend" id="arrowLegend">
            <div style="color:#ff4757">â— ç´…è‰²ï¼šä¸‹æ»‘æ¨åŠ› (sinåˆ†åŠ›)</div>
            <div style="color:#38bdf8">â— è—è‰²ï¼šè»Œé“å£“åŠ› (cosåˆ†åŠ›)</div>
        </div>
        <br>
        
        <button class="btn-start" id="startBtn">ğŸš€ é³´ç¬›å•Ÿå‹•æ¸¬è©¦</button>
        <button id="viewBtn">ğŸ¥ åˆ‡æ›è¦–è§’ (V)</button>
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 10px; margin-top: 10px;">
            <button id="addCar" style="background:#444; font-size:11px; width:50%">è»Šå»‚ +</button>
            <button id="removeCar" style="background:#444; font-size:11px; width:50%">è»Šå»‚ -</button>
        </div>
        <hr>
        <div class="info-row"><span>ç‹€æ…‹ï¼š</span><span id="status-text" class="data">æº–å‚™å°±ç·’</span></div>
        <div class="info-row"><span>æ™‚é€Ÿï¼š</span><span id="speed-val" class="data">0</span> km/h</div>
    </div>
